metadata.name: I Am Rich
metadata.description:
In 2008 an iPhone app called “I am Rich” appeared and offered no features at all for $999 (0.62 eth). It was purely a flex & sold 8 copies. Can history repeat itself in this Open Edition Mint capped at 8. 

I Am Rich is an NFT that serves no purpose other than to show off your wealth. With the purchase of this NFT, you can be sure to flex your financial success to the world. The I Am Rich NFT is a digital asset that symbolizes your wealth and status. It is an exclusive item that only a select few can own. Don't miss out on your chance to show off your riches and be part of a select group of individuals who own an I Am Rich NFT.
